thread.title: UPS Earnings: What to Watch

author: Paul Ziobro
title: UPS Earnings: What to Watch
text:
United Parcel Service Inc. is scheduled to release its fourth-quarter results before the market opens Thursday. Here is what you need to know.
EARNINGS FORECAST: Analysts polled by Thomson Reuters expect UPS to earn $1.66 a share, compared with $1.63 a share a year ago. Based on the companyâ€™s full-year forecast, UPS projects EPS between $1.51 and $1.76 for the quarter.
